# Ticket CSV Template
#
# Compatible with both JIRA CSV Import and Azure DevOps CSV Import.
#
# JIRA Import: Project Settings → External System Import → CSV
# ADO Import:  Queries → Import Work Items → CSV
#
# Notes:
#   - Story Points may map to a custom field in JIRA (check config)
#   - Acceptance Criteria is appended to Description for JIRA (no standard field)
#   - For ADO, Acceptance Criteria maps to Microsoft.VSTS.Common.AcceptanceCriteria
#   - Labels use semicolons as separator in the CSV
#   - Priority values: Highest, High, Medium, Low, Lowest (JIRA) or 1-4 (ADO)
#
# Columns:
Summary,Issue Type,Priority,Story Points,Labels,Description,Acceptance Criteria
"{summary}","{issue_type}","{priority}",{story_points},"{labels}","{description}","{acceptance_criteria}"
